QUESTION OF THE DAY:

This one is strictly for the coaches.

HAVE YOU EVER HAD A CLIENT ATTEMPT TO BLAME YOU FOR THEIR POOR PLACING IN A SHOW? WHEN IN REALITY, THEY JUST COULDN’T AFFORD TO PROPERLY PREPARE? 

I could see if we didn’t explain the costs involved with competing. We as coaches can only explain the expenses for bodybuilding so many times. And some clients are so dead-set on competing “RIGHT NOW”, instead of waiting until they can actually AFFORD to prepare properly. So you as a coach, can only do the best you can with what that client can afford. If that client can’t afford the costs associated with bodybuilding, how is it YOUR fault when they don’t place as well as “they” expected. We as coaches, can only do so much. 
.
I keep it real:
IF YOU CAN’T AFFORD THE FOOD, THE SUPPLEMENTS, THE COACHING, THE COMPETITION FEES, THE REGISTRATION FEES, ETC, THEN BODYBUILDING ISN’T FOR YOU!🤷🏾‍♂️
#facts #nuffsaid #sorrynotsorry #realtalk #keepitreal #keepit💯 #explorepage
